Braithwaite: &quot;Messi? When you know him and you're close to him, you can see that he's just one of the boys. He's quiet, calm and completely down to earth. He likes to have fun and he just wants to play football because he loves it.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;We have an amazing team spirit. A dressing room with a lot of turmoil wouldn't be able to come back in games. We stand together and feel fantastic as a squad.&quot;
